               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Sǝnkǝssar “Synaxarion” for the first half of the year (fols.
                     2ra-181vb)
 I-1) Maskaram (fols. 2ra – 30vc)
 I-2) Ṭǝqǝmt (fols. 31ra –
                     55rc)
 I-3) Ḫǝdār (fols. 55va – 82va)
 I-4) Tāḫśāś (fols. 83ra
                     –115vc)
 I-5) Ṭǝrr (fols. 116ra – 155vb)
 I-6) Yakkātit (fols. 156ra –
                     181vb)
 The commemorative notices are followed by ʿarke-hymns
 
                     Additiones 1-2.</summary>
