                           165ra.
 - Erasures without marking: e.g., <locus target="#93rb">93rb</locus>, 97va, 131vb.
 - Crude drawings, scribbels in pen
                           and pencil: e.g., <locus target="#1r">1r</locus>, 1v, 8r, 50r, 51r,
                           158v,176v, 181vc.</item>
                        <item xml:id="e2">
                           <desc type="findingAid">- The names of the months are written in the upper
                              margin of some fols. (the black ink is of a different tone): ወርኀ መስከረም
                              ቡሩክ(?): <locus target="#2r">fol. 2r</locus> ወርኀ ጥቅምት ቡሩክ: <locus target="#31r">fol. 31r</locus> ወርኀ ኅዳር ቡሩክ: <locus target="#55v">fol. 55v</locus> ዝንቱ ወርኀ ታኅሣሥ: <locus target="#83r">fol.
                                 83r</locus> ወርኀ ጥር: <locus target="#116r">fol. 116r</locus> ወርኀ
                              የካቲት: <locus target="#156r">fol. 156r</locus>. All names are encircled
                              with a red line (fols. 2r, 31r) or with red dots (fols. 55v, 156r) or
